      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i already talked to my doctor and they basically just said \"we'll see how it goes\" and didn't really give me a clear answer. i'm just worried about the sertraline not being enough. since st johns wort is just a herbal supplement and not a drug, i figured it would just be a mild boost rather than something that actually interferes with the medicine. is there really a big risk if i just take a low dose for a few days to see how i feel?",
